Interface IProcessorMatcher<T extends Node>

All Known Subinterfaces:
IAttributeNameProcessorMatcher, ICommentNodeProcessorMatcher, IDocumentNodeProcessorMatcher, IElementNameProcessorMatcher, ITextNodeProcessorMatcher
All Known Implementing Classes:
AttributeNameProcessorMatcher, CommentNodeProcessorMatcher, DocumentNodeProcessorMatcher, ElementNameProcessorMatcher, TextNodeProcessorMatcher
public interface IProcessorMatcher<T extends Node>

Common interface for objects that specify when a processor can be applied to a node.

Since:
2.0.0
Author:
Daniel Fernández
